 <H1>Scenario: Web Portfolio Manager</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>Latency: Observation = ~0 (triggered by update 15 mins after stock prices change), Delivery = HTTP connection
</H2>
</UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Intermediation: Portfolio Server computes total portfolio value before sending information to the client
</H2>
</UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Initiator: Portfolio Server receives �pushed� quotes from Stock Server, does recalculation, then initiates with client
</H2>
</UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Delivery Constraints: Reliable Connection
</H2>
</UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Notification Management:
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Client subscription request enumerates current holdings</UL></UL></P>
